# Project Overview

DCM Utilities — shared scripts and tooling for the [dcm-project](https://github.com/dcm-project) ecosystem.
Currently houses the E2E deploy script; will also contain the E2E test suite.

**For non-Cursor environments:** See `CLAUDE.md` at project root for consolidated context.

## Key Directories
- `scripts/` - Shell scripts (deploy, teardown, health checks)
- `.github/workflows/` - CI configuration (ShellCheck linting)
- `.cursor/rules/` - AI context rules (auto-loaded by Cursor)
- `.cursor/prompts/` - Task-specific guides (use with `@` in Cursor)

## Important
This repo contains **bash scripts, not Go code**. There is no build step or compiled output.

## Available Prompts
Use `@<prompt-name>` in Cursor to include task-specific context:
- `@deploy-dcm` - Deploy the full DCM stack
- `@tear-down` - Tear down a running DCM deployment
- `@check-versions` - Get running container versions
- `@troubleshoot-deploy` - Diagnose deployment issues
- `@maintain-pr-summary` - Maintain a running PR summary document
